Dialogs.Dialog: 小早川
...Rise and shine.
Hmm... Gimme 5 more hours...
Hah. I took the trouble to come here and wake you up. Come on, snap out of it！
Hmm...？
Huh？ ▲小早川＊▲！ Why are you here？
You said you could barely wake up in the morning, so I'm here to help.
I did？
Geez... I've come really far just for you, and now you're giving me that attitude.
Sorry, sorry.
If you don't hurry, we're going to be late.
Oh, right.
I can't be here every morning to wake you up, you know？
小早川
I said wake up.
Just a little. Just a little more...
Come on！
Hmm...？
▲小早川＊▲！？ Eh？ Why are you...？
Are you going to sleep in again？ I told you I'd be coming to wake you up, right？
I... did？
Have you forgotten already？ Whatever, just do as you like then.
Sorry, sorry... But... having ▲小早川＊▲ come wake me up...
Come again？
It feels like we're a married couple, eh？
Don't get over your head！ Get back to sleep！
Ouch.
Come on, snap out of it！
(Make up you mind...)
小早川
Come on... Wake up... Just wake up...
Umm... Just a little bit. Just a little bit more...
Geez... If you're going to be like this, we'll be late, you know？
Ah, you woke up.
▲小早川＊▲？ Why are you here？
I told you that I'd wake you up in the morning, right？
Ah, that's... right.
I've promised you... Have you forgotten？
Sorry, sorry.
You're really bad at waking up, I guess. Was the good morning kiss not enough for you？
K-Kiss！？ No way... You did？ When I was asleep？
Kidding. I don't mind if you want to. Hehe.
小早川
Come on, wake up.
Umm... Few more minutes...
If you don't wake up soon, Rinko will go ahead！！！？
...Mmm. ▲小早川＊▲, wait for me！
Hmph. Rinko will wait forever just for you, you know？ What a lucky boyfriend.
小早川
...Come on, wake up. Wake up or Rinko will go ahead.
Mmm... Ah！ ▲小早川＊▲... Good morning.
Rinko is not your mother！
Right, sorry.
Hey, hurry and get ready, okay？
小早川
Good~ morning~♪
Hmm？
Whoa！ You surprised me！ ▲小早川＊▲...
So, are you wide awake now？
Yeah, but you really surprised me.
Hehe, I never thought that waking you up could be so much fun.
小早川
Hey.
What's the matter？
I made lunch.
Wow, that would be nice if Iget the chance to eat ▲小早川＊▲'s cooking.
Wait...
Hmm？
This is for you！ Take it！
Wow！ This is amazing.
I'm new at this stuff. Is the menu okay？
Yeah, it's totally okay. Wow, ▲小早川＊▲ can make Japanese dishes. That's surprising.
What do you mean by surprising？ ...Well, I made it based on reference, so I'll forgive you.
(Reference, huh？ She really tried her best...)
小早川
Hey, wait up.
Oh, ▲小早川＊▲. What's up？
I just happened to make you some lunch. Here.
▲小早川＊▲ did！？
Whoa！ This is... You made this all by yourself？
Yup, even though I don't do this often, I put some effort into it this time. What do you think？
I'm really happy.
Whoa, a Japanese-style dish... The combination is just right. It will surely attract the eyes of a commoner...
That was unnecessary！
小早川
Hey, hey.
Ah, ▲小早川＊▲. How did you spend your lunchtime？
Today is a special day, hehe.
You look pretty cheerful today.
Tada~！ Rinko made lunch for you！
Really？ Cool！
It's a Japanese-style lunch. What do you think？
Yeah, I'm very happy. ▲小早川＊▲ really knows how to cook, eh？
Hehe. Just a little. So, does it make Rinko look better in your eyes？ Don't you want Rinko to be your bride？
Yeah. I think ▲小早川＊▲ will be a good wife.
The truth is, I've been preparing hard for today. Hehe.
(Aaawww... That's so cute.)
小早川
Okay, here's your lunch. I made you a Japanese- style one.
Oh, thank you. I think it's getting better every time.
So, is it delicious？
Yeah, it sure is. ▲小早川＊▲'s seasoning is getting better and better.
I'll continue making it for you then.
小早川
Hey, here's your lunch.
I'm so impressed with it every time... This one is also great.
Well, that's good. I made this with confidence.
(Something like this is very nice...)
小早川
Here's your lunch.
Thanks. I think ▲小早川＊▲ is really good at cooking.
Really？ Do you see any improvement？
Yeah, it's getting better every time. I can't wait to see what you'll make next.
Yeah！ I'll do my best on my next Love-Love Lunch Box！
小早川
...Hey.
Oh, ▲小早川＊▲. What's up？
Hmm... Rinko brought a lunch box today？ Shall we eat together？
Okay. Then I'll go buy something.
No, I didn't mean that...
Hehe... I put some effort in it. What do you think？
You really made this by yourself？
Well, if it's just a sandwich, Rinko can make it well.
Yeah, not bad. Nice job.
You sounded like my teacher with his evaluation. Can't you show more appreciation？
Well... Thank you. I'm really happy.
Yup, since you thanked me properly, I won't punish you.
小早川
Hey, wait. Wait.
Eh？ ▲小早川＊▲. What's up？
Today is special, all right？
Why？
Rinko made lunch for you.
Really？ I'm happy. ▲小早川＊▲'s special lunch, eh？
Don't say special！ It's just a regular sandwich after all.
But you've done very well.
Really？ Well, if it's just this, Rinko can handle it.
▲小早川＊▲！ really made it specially for me after all.
Stop saying unnecessary things and just eat quietly！
小早川
Hey. Um...
Huh？ What's up？
Hehe, you should be happy. Today's a special day.
What day is it today...？
Whoa, all of this... Did ▲小早川＊▲ make it？
Of course！ But it's actually just a regular sandwich.
Yeah, you can't tell some people by the sandwiches they made. Thank you.
Are you trying to start a fight？ Geez.
(Wrong words to show my gratitude？)
小早川
Here, your lunch.
Thanks. It always gives me a power boost.
Why don't you try the seasoning first？
...Yeah, so delicious！
You have ketchup all over your mouth... Aren't you just like a little kid？
小早川
Here.
Thanks. It tastes even better than the first sandwich you made.
Really？ So, is it good？
Yeah, delicious.
I'll continue making them for you then.
小早川
Here, your lunch.
Oh. I'm always looking forward to this.
This time is a special Western-style menu. I practiced every day just to make this.
You make me very happy. Thanks.
Hehe. Aren't you grateful having Rinko as your girlfriend？
小早川
Hey, just a moment.
What's the matter, ▲小早川＊▲？
The truth is... I made lunch for you...
For me？
I don't see anyone else around here... I don't know if you'll like it though.
Whoa, it looks great！ Chinese style？
You don't like Chinese food？
No way！ I love Chinese food！
Good then... Will you try to eat it？
Of course, I'll eat until there's nothing left.
You must. That's your responsibility after all.
小早川
Hey, just a moment.
▲小早川＊▲？ What's the matter？ Why are you here？
Somehow, Mom made some extra food for lunch. So Rinko brought it over, for you.
Oh really？ I appreciate it so much. Tell her I'm so grateful, okay？
I can't... guarantee the taste, okay？
It won't be that bad！ I'll eat it gratefully！
Chinese style, huh？ Yeah, it's very delicious.
Really？ Then this is worth my effort to wake up very early and try my best...
Try your best？
I mean, Mom had tried her best！
▲小早川＊▲？
小早川
Hehe. Today I have something nice for you.
What would that be？ Another flying kick？
Hey, it's not that. A lunch box, you know... I made this for you.
Really？
Whoa, Chinese food！
I'm still not good at making them though...
Don't be like that. It's not bad at all, okay？
Really？ Then after this, I'll learn from more recipes.
小早川
Here, your lunch box. It's Chinese food again.
Whoa, thanks. I think you've gotten really good at making them.
So, is it delicious？
Of course. They're exquisitely flavored！
What's with that "exquisitely flavored" thingy...？ Well, I get what you mean, though.
小早川
Here's your lunch. Today is Chinese food.
Thank you. I really like this, you know？
You didn't expect them at all, did you？
Yeah. The taste is gradually getting better with each bite.
R-Really？ I'll try to make them again then.
小早川
Here's your lunch. I tried Chinese food this time.
Thank you. Hmm, it tastes delicious.
I guess... it will feel like this when we're married...
Eh！？
It's just a possibility. We can't be impatient.
